abstract: Thirteen people were wounded in a shooting at a party on Chicago's south side intended to honor the victim of an earlier shooting, police said.
snippet: Thirteen people were wounded in a shooting at a party on Chicago's south side intended to honor the victim of an earlier shooting, police said.
lead_paragraph: (Reuters) - Thirteen people were wounded in a shooting at a party on Chicago's south side intended to honor the victim of an earlier shooting, police said.
headline_main: Party to Honor Chicago Shooting Victim Ends With 13 Wounded: Police
headline_print_headline: Party to Honor Chicago Shooting Victim Ends With 13 Wounded: Police
